	   <tr><td colspan=2>I can summerize EQ in 2 statements...<br><br>1.) it is the most well thought out MMORPG out there, and may very well be the best designed RPG EVER. It is enjoyable, has near infinite replayability, and is just about anything you could ever ask for in a game.<br><br>This makes this next statement even harsher.<br><br>2.) It is run by a company that cares exactly jack and @#%^ about it's players. They know the type of people that play their game and they know that it's not the type of person who's going to stand up against them unless they really go WAY to far... so they run roughshod over you. Don't forget their motto 'your in our world now'. That has more ooc meaning then ic meaning in this game.<br><br>Those two statements summerize all EQ for you.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
